  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IconMarker
    This class extends Marker and draws an icon instead of a circle for it's visual representation.
    Marker
    This class will represent a physical location and will calculate it's visibility and draw it's text and visual representation accordingly.
    Radar
    This class will visually represent a radar screen with a radar radius and blips on the screen in their appropriate locations.
